data.description:
1737 sq ft two story home sitting on 1 acre. 3 bedroom and 2 bath. All electric home. Gas log fireplace with its own tank. Jetted tub. Remodeled in 2020. 26g metal roof and gutters in 2018. Kitchen appliances new in 2017. Large two car garage. 4x6 steel storm shelter placed in garage in 2021.
Concrete patios front and rear. Large chain link fence. Aerobic septic system with sprinklers.
30x50x14 insulated shop with a 20x30 lean-to. 6+ inch concrete in shop. 200 amp service. 5 ton HVAC unit. Half bath.
24x12 metal storage building.
7.5x10 storage building.
Bolt internet.
918-533-0480 to schedule an appointment.
Address is 12571 S Hwy 125, Miami OK 74354
